    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Helper class to incorporate basic object transformation feature into plugins User can move objects by dragging them, rotate by dragging with Ctrl key; scaling is disabled by default To use, create class instance and call its event handlers For extra features, override the <computeroutput>pick_</computeroutput> method </para>
